SIMPLE: seventieth
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Seventieth
<hw>Sev"en*ti*eth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
hund-<ets>seofontigo⟦edh⟧a</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Next in order
after the sixty-ninth; <as>as, a man in the <ex>seventieth</ex> year of
his age</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Constituting or being one of seventy equal
parts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seventieth</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Seventieth
<hw>Sev"en*ti*eth</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One next in order
after the sixty-ninth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The quotient of a unit divided by seventy; one of
seventy equal parts or fractions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seventy</ent>⟦br⟧
